## Environment Variables
PORT=3001
JWT_KEY=conduit-demo-secret-change-me

## Development Database (SQLite — 无需安装数据库服务器，开箱即用)
## 仓库已附带种子库 conduit-dev.sqlite（含示例用户与文章），直接启动即可
DEV_DB_DIALECT=sqlite
DEV_DB_STORAGE=./conduit-dev.sqlite
DEV_DB_NAME=database_development
DEV_DB_LOGGING=false

## Testing Database (SQLite 内存库)
TEST_DB_DIALECT=sqlite
TEST_DB_STORAGE=:memory:
TEST_DB_NAME=database_testing
TEST_DB_LOGGING=false

## Production Database (如需 postgres/mysql 自行改 DIALECT 与连接参数)
PROD_DB_DIALECT=sqlite
PROD_DB_STORAGE=./conduit-prod.sqlite
PROD_DB_NAME=database_production
PROD_DB_LOGGING=false
